A sleek black smartwatch with a glossy touchscreen display rests on a polished dark marble surface, captured in dramatic studio lighting with sharp reflections. The watch face glows with an abstract colorful interface pattern. In the soft-focused background, the curved glass windows of an airport duty-free shop create bokeh light spots. The composition emphasizes the premium materials and futuristic design of early wearable technology, shot from a low angle to make the device appear iconic and desirable. Photorealistic style with cinematic depth of field and rich contrast between the deep blacks of the watch and warm ambient lighting.
